# Amazon Clone Frontend Environment Variables

# Backend API URL
# For local development: http://localhost:5000
# For production (Render): https://amazon-clone-backend-c615.onrender.com
VITE_API_URL=https://amazon-clone-backend-c615.onrender.com

# Note: If not set, the app will automatically use:
# - http://localhost:5000 for local development (npm run dev)
# - https://amazon-clone-backend-c615.onrender.com for production
